===Noun===
'''toss'''
#a [[throw]], a [[lob]], of a ball etc., with an intial upward direction (often implying a lack of care)
#the toss of a coin before a cricket, football etc. match

===Verb===
'''to toss'''

#to throw with an intial upward direction
#to [[flip]] a coin
#to discard
#to [[stir]] or [[mix]] (used only for [[salad]])


